<p><img class='alignnone' alt='' src='./ff3_images/ff3_part_1-2/04-castle_sasune-006.png' width='486' height='326' /><br /> <span style='color: #ffffff;'>-</span><br /> <span style='color: #ffffff;'>-</span><br /> 頂層還有一個寶箱：<span style='color: #800000;'>屠屍劍</span> ( 開啟後會遇敵 )</p>
